-- Persian Gulf Equity Movers: Dubai Investments, Almarai, NMTC
-- B y   A r i f   S h a r i f
-- 2013-09-04T14:55:44Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-09-04/persian-gulf-equity-movers-dubai-investments-almarai-nmtc.html
Dubai’s DFM General Index drops 3.7%
to 2,396.79 at close in Dubai, lowest close since July 11, as 23
shrs fall and 8 are unchanged; Abu Dhabi’s ADX -2.3%, Kuwait’s
SE Index -2.6%, Qatar’s QE Index -1.9%; Saudi Tadawul All Share
Index -2.2%.  ADVANCERS:
* National Mobile Telecommunication (NMTC KK) +1%, most since
July 24, biggest gainer on Kuwait index by pts.  DECLINERS:
* Dubai Investments (DIC UH) -5.3%, lowest since July 11
* Dubai Islamic Bank (DIB UH) -4.9% to lowest since June 30
* Almarai Co. (ALMARAI AB) -3.3% to lowest since July 29; co.
plans to sell perpetual Islamic bonds  To contact the reporter on this story:
